<p>Thus, we have just released ExpressionEngine 3.5.13, the final &#8220;normal&#8221; patch release for version 3. It includes a small handful of bug fixes and adds PHP 7.2 compatibility. You can find details in the <a href="https://docs.expressionengine.com/v3/about/changelog.html#version-3-5-13">ExpressionEngine 3 change log</a>.</p>
