				<p>We still love ExpressionEngine version 3 even if version 4 is on the near horizon!</p>

<p>Thus we present over a dozen bug fixes and some nifty optimizations.</p>

<p>Deleting Sites will no longer cause issues with member assignments.  Be sure and update to this release before deleting a Site or you&#8217;ll need to re-assign some permissions.</p>

<p>The live look button is back, and the forum permission settings are now more cooperative.  You may see a speed improvement in the publish form if you&#8217;re using lots of categories, and developers should enjoy the new <code>URL_TITLE_MAX_LENGTH</code> constant and some cleaning up in the DocBlocks.</p>

<p>See the <a href="https://docs.expressionengine.com/v3/about/changelog.html#version-3-5-12">changelog</a> for the full list of improvements or just go <a href="https://expressionengine.com/store/purchases">download it now</a>.</p>

