<p>We are happy to announce that Solspace&#8217;s Freeform Next and Freeform Next Pro are available in the <a href="https://expressionengine.com/store#freeform-next">ExpressionEngine store</a>.</p>

<p>Freeform Next lets you build great forms for your ExpressionEngine site with custom notifications. With Freeform Next forms you can collect and react to visitor interactions with ease. They are easy to build, powerful, and the Pro version even includes API integrations with popular CRM and mailing list¬†services like Salesforce and MailChimp.</p>

<p>Solspace is one of ExpressionEngine&#8217;s oldest and most trusted add-on providers, with over ten years experience extending the platform. Freeform Next is the latest evolution of one of their most popular ExpressionEngine add-ons.</p>

<p>Every purchase of Freeform Next comes with 1 year of premium support from the Solspace team. And you can manage and download your ExpressionEngine and Freeform Next licenses all from your ExpressionEngine.com account.</p>

<p>Head on over the store and <a href="https://expressionengine.com/store#freeform-next">grab Freeform Next</a> for your next project or site enhancement!</p>

